---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for Resurgence Builds — how we handle your data.">
  <div class="container section content-width">
    <h1 class="heading-accent">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--ink-muted);">Last updated: April 20, 2026</p>
    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Introduction</h2>
      <p>Resurgence Builds ("we," "our," or "us") operates the website resurgencebuilds.com. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our site.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <h3>Automatically Collected</h3>
      <p>We use privacy-respecting analytics (Plausible Analytics) that collects no personal data. We may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Page views and referral sources (aggregated, no cookies)</li>
        <li>Country-level geolocation (no IP storage)</li>
        <li>Device type and browser (aggregated)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Voluntarily Provided</h3>
      <p>If you subscribe to our newsletter via Buttondown, we collect your email address solely for sending updates. You can unsubscribe at any time.</p>

      <h2>GDPR Rights (EU Users)</h2>
      <p>Under GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Rectify inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Erase your data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
        <li>Restrict processing</li>
        <li>Data portability</li>
        <li>Object to processing</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@resurgencebuilds.com">legal@resurgencebuilds.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>CalOPPA Compliance (California Users)</h2>
      <p>We do not sell personal information. We do not track users across third-party websites. We honor Do Not Track browser signals. California residents may request details about data we hold by contacting us.</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>We do not use tracking cookies. Our analytics (Plausible) is cookie-free. Third-party services (Google Fonts) may set their own cookies per their policies.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Hosting and CDN</li>
        <li><strong>Plausible Analytics:</strong> Privacy-respecting analytics</li>
        <li><strong>Buttondown:</strong> Newsletter delivery</li>
        <li><strong>Google Fonts:</strong> Typography</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>We serve all content over HTTPS with HSTS enabled. We do not store passwords, payment information, or sensitive personal data.</p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy. Changes will be posted here with an updated date.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:legal@resurgencebuilds.com">legal@resurgencebuilds.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
